{"tid":2035590,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港股中午升429點 港元拆息全線回落","createTime":"2020-05-26T04:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T04:34:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b223d26ec8efe6477c0a9bde37204a9c3bc69689","tid":2035590,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:26:34.000Z","msg":"港股中午升429點　美團急升8%再破頂<br />\n26.05.2020 12:20<br />\n<br />\n港股跟隨外圍及內地股市造好，恒生指數高開246點，其後升幅擴大至逾400點，高見23409點，中午收報23381點，升429點，升幅1.9%，成交額580億元。國企指數報9614點，升148點，升幅1.5%。<br />\n<br />\n藍籌股全線向上，本地地產股有反彈，恒基地產(<a href=\"http://00012.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00012.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=0b17cdc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00012.HK</a>)終止連續4日跌勢，中午升近5%，報28.25元，升1.3元，是半日升幅最大藍籌，新地(<a href=\"http://00016.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00016.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=77553bb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00016.HK</a>)升3%，報92元，升2.9元，恒隆地產(<a href=\"http://00101.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00101.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=ce3fd024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00101.HK</a>)升逾2%，報16.3元。內房股亦上升，華潤置地(<a href=\"http://01109.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01109.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=14b98fde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01109.HK</a>)升逾3%，報30.3元，中國恒大(<a href=\"http://03333.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03333.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=fb807ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03333.HK</a>)升4%，報16.84元，碧桂園(<a href=\"http://02007.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02007.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=244611dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02007.HK</a>)升3%，報9.58元。<br />\n<br />\n新經濟股造好，美團點評(<a href=\"http://03690.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03690.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=fb709bd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03690.HK</a>)業績後被券商上調目標價，股價再破頂，一度急升逾9%，高見138元，中午升8%，報136.3元，升10.5元。騰訊(<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=a22ed99d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>)升逾1%，報423.4元，阿里巴巴(<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=fb132e28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>)升2%，報202.4元。近月急升的康希諾生物(<a href=\"http://06185.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F06185.HK&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=3e5302bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">06185.HK</a>)持續有回吐，股價急跌逾9%，報173.1元，跌18元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290538&amp;csid=261_368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1290538%26csid%3D261_368&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=f69ce080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290538&amp;csid=261_368</a><br />\n<br />\n港元拆息全線回落　一個月拆息跌至0.96厘<br />\n26.05.2020 11:54<br />\n<br />\n港元拆息全線回落，隔夜息報0.24厘，回落5個點子，一星期拆息報0.67厘，回落34個點子，用作按息的一個月拆息，降至0.96厘，回落16點子。長息方面，六個月拆息1.44厘，回落7個點子，十二個月拆息1.59厘，回落9個點子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290532&amp;csid=261_368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1290532%26csid%3D261_368&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=f1523666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290532&amp;csid=261_368</a>"},{"pid":"7c0b5cee68942fd208a2ef23fa1e6bb366fd5ed1","tid":2035590,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"冇事！回復正常了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074375c5fa53fd63cc3296a5625ec3ff81ce35e0","tid":2035590,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:32:32.000Z","msg":"撤資？驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc790d0a3b76b2bd81645052a4d06990229bf00","tid":2035590,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:34:43.000Z","msg":"唔知頂到幾耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}